article_id:441,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Displayed Might and Actual Might,image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue where the might values displayed in the team menu and the actual might values stored on the game&#39;s server are not equal.</div><div><br></div><div>Please try to change your equipped weapons, wyrmprints and dragons in the team menu if any of the situations below occur:</div><div><br></div><div>・You cannot start a quest even though your team&#39;s might is higher than the required might for said quest.</div><div>・You cannot clear might-related endeavors even though your team&#39;s might is higher than said endeavors&#39; might requirements.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue. Any further updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1556290500,update_time1556296522